WEBVTT

00:07:30.917 --> 00:07:33.417
And that was a really
important lesson for me.

00:07:34.625 --> 00:07:35.976
The second lesson

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:40.684
is that when we sit down to negotiate

00:07:40.708 --> 00:07:42.434
with the enemy,

00:07:42.458 --> 00:07:45.768
we need to remember,
there's a human being in front of us

00:07:45.792 --> 00:07:49.268
that very likely
has more in common with us

00:07:49.292 --> 00:07:51.601
than we care to admit.

00:07:51.625 --> 00:07:53.018
And I learned this firsthand

00:07:53.042 --> 00:07:57.393
when I was invited to visit
at a major poultry company's headquarters.

00:07:57.417 --> 00:08:01.434
And it was the first time
that my organization had been invited,